    [
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "4) (25 points) The scientists FitzHugh (1961) and Nagumo, Arimoto, Yoshizawa (1962) derived a mathematical model to characterize the behavior of a neuron under the externally injected current "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "I"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ": "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                134,
                85,
                907,
                115
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "equation_interline",
            "content": {
                "math_content": "\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} \\frac {d V}{d t} & = V - \\frac {1}{3} V ^ {3} - W + I, \\\\ \\frac {d W}{d t} & = \\frac {1}{\\tau} \\big (V + a - b W \\big), \\end{array} \\right.",
                "math_type": "latex",
                "image_source": {
                    "path": "images/920295b53379494e9bb23e942f2505b73c2b5f01e1a5852c95e79955afd45687.jpg"
                }
            },
            "bbox": [
                428,
                126,
                640,
                162
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "where the variable "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "V"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "describes the membrane potential of the neuron, the variable "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "W"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "describes the current arising from opening and closing of ion channels on the neurons membrane. The variables "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\tau"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ", "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "a"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "and "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "b"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "are parameters with typical values: a = 0.7, "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "b = 0 . 8"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "and "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\tau = 1 3"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ". "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                156,
                172,
                910,
                215
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "list",
            "content": {
                "list_type": "text_list",
                "list_items": [
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "( i )"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "For a small positive constant current "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "I"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ", how the neuron behaves. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "( i i )"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "For a large positive constant current "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "I"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ", how the neuron behaves. "
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "item_type": "text",
                        "item_content": [
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "( i i i )"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "Suppose one injects a pulse current with different magnitude at some time "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "t _ { 0 }"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ", i.e., "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "I = I _ { 0 } \\delta ( t - t _ { 0 } )"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": ", where "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "I _ { 0 }"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "describes the magnitude of the pulse, analyze the dynamical behavior of the neuron when "
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "equation_inline",
                                "content": "I _ { 0 }"
                            },
                            {
                                "type": "text",
                                "content": "， is small or large. "
                            }
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                156,
